  title="Maturity Number in Numerology: Your Second-Half Blueprint | Numerology Guides"
  description="Your maturity number reveals who you're growing into after age 35. Learn how to calculate it from your Life Path and Expression Numbers, and what each maturity number means."
>

  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600&display=swap" />
  <style>
    :root { --font-family-heading: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; }
