      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
      <span style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-weight:600;">Maturity Number</span>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:6rem 1.5rem 5rem;text-align:center;min-height:480px;display:flex;align-items:center;">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:0;">
      <img
        src="/images/learn/Maturity Numbers Pillar Hero.webp"
        alt=""
        aria-hidden="true"
        fetchpriority="high"
        style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 30%;display:block;"
      />
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(14,10,26,0.75) 0%, rgba(14,10,26,0.58) 45%, rgba(14,10,26,0.80) 100%);"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(196,162,78,0.08) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:28px 28px;pointer-events:none;"></div>
    </div>
    <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:-1rem;top:0.5rem;z-index:1;font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-size:clamp(10rem,20vw,16rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(196,162,78,0.18);pointer-events:none;user-select:none;">M</div>
    <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;right:-0.5rem;bottom:-1.5rem;z-index:1;font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-size:clamp(12rem,24vw,20rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(124,92,191,0.15);pointer-events:none;user-select:none;">N</div>
    <div style="position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;">
      <p class="p-label" style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;color:var(--color-soft-gold);opacity:0.9;">Core Number</p>
      <div class="p-divider" style="margin-bottom:1.75rem;"></div>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-size:clamp(2.6rem,6.5vw,4.75rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.08;color:#f5f0e8;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:0 0 1.5rem;text-shadow:0 2px 20px rgba(14,10,26,0.6);">
        Maturity Number in<br><em style="color:#c8a8f0;font-style:italic;">Numerology</em>
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(240,234,255,0.82);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;text-shadow:0 1px 8px rgba(14,10,26,0.5);">
        Your maturity number is who you're becoming. It's the energy that kicks in after 35, the slow reveal of the person you were always growing into.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.875rem;justify-content:center;">
        <a href="https://8904b5z1168aar3k8annz7y61n.hop.clickbank.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:var(--color-violet);color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.15s;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(124,92,191,0.45);" onmouseover="this.style.background='#6a4eab';this.style.transform='translateY(-1px)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--color-violet)';this.style.transform='none'">Get My Free Reading →</a>
        <a href="#what" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);color:#f5f0e8;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;padding:0.875rem 1.75rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);transition:border-color 0.2s,background 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.15)';this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.4)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.08)';this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.2)'">Explore ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Author byline -->
  <div style="background:var(--color-light-bg);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;">
      <img src="/images/author-maddi-green.webp" alt="Maddie Greene" style="width:2.75rem;height:2.75rem;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;flex-shrink:0;border:2px solid rgba(124,92,191,0.2);" />
      <div>
        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 0.1rem;">Written by <strong>Maddie Greene</strong></p>
        <p style="color:var(--color-muted-text);font-size:0.78rem;margin:0;">Numerology writer &amp; researcher</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content + Sticky sidebar wrapper -->
  <div class="xl:flex xl:gap-6 xl:max-w-[1200px] xl:mx-auto xl:px-4">
    <!-- Main content column -->
    <div class="xl:flex-1 xl:min-w-0">

  <!-- Main content -->
  <article style="padding:2.5rem 1.5rem 3rem;background:white;">
    <div style="max-width:48rem;margin:0 auto;">

      <!-- What is the maturity number -->
      <section id="what" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <h2 class="section-h2">What is the maturity number?</h2>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          Most numerology numbers describe who you are right now. Your <a href="/learn/life-path-number/" style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);">life path number</a> is what you came in with. Your <a href="/learn/expression-number/" style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);">expression number</a> is the direction you're moving toward. But the maturity number is different. It describes who you're becoming, specifically the person who shows up in the second half of your life.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          Think of it like a slow reveal. For the first 35–40 years, your life path and expression energies are doing their thing separately. One shapes your instincts. The other shapes your goals. But somewhere around midlife, those two streams merge. And the result is your maturity number, the energy that emerges when your innate nature and your life direction have had enough time to blend together.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          It's sometimes called the "True Self" number, and there's a good reason for that. The maturity number isn't who you were told to be. It isn't who you performed as in your twenties. It's who you actually are once the noise quiets down and the real priorities surface.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;">
          Here's the thing: a lot of people experience their maturity number as relief. They describe feeling more comfortable in their own skin after 40. More clear about what matters. Less interested in proving things and more interested in building things. That's the maturity number doing its work.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- How to calculate -->
      <section id="calculate" style="margin-bottom:3rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <h2 class="section-h2">How to calculate your maturity number</h2>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          The formula is straightforward. Take your <a href="/learn/life-path-number/" style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);">Life Path Number</a> and add it to your <a href="/learn/expression-number/" style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);">Expression Number</a>. Then reduce the result to a single digit, unless it's 11, 22, or 33. Those are master numbers and you keep them as-is.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          That's it. Two numbers you already have, added together.
        </p>

        <div class="card-light p-6" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
          <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-body-text);margin:0 0 0.75rem;">Example 1</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Life Path Number: <strong>7</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Expression Number: <strong>5</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">7 + 5 = 12</p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">1 + 2 = <strong>3</strong>. Maturity number is <strong>3</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-light p-6" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
          <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-body-text);margin:0 0 0.75rem;">Example 2</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Life Path Number: <strong>9</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Expression Number: <strong>8</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">9 + 8 = 17</p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">1 + 7 = <strong>8</strong>. Maturity number is <strong>8</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-light p-6" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-body-text);margin:0 0 0.75rem;">Example 3 (Master Number)</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Life Path Number: <strong>4</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">Expression Number: <strong>7</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">4 + 7 = <strong>11</strong></p>
          <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">Stop here. 11 is a master number. Maturity number is <strong>11</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;">
          Don't know your life path or expression number yet? You can <a href="/calculator/" style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);">use our calculator</a> to find both, then add them together for your maturity number.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- All maturity number meanings -->
      <section id="meanings" style="margin-bottom:3rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <h2 class="section-h2">All maturity number meanings</h2>

        <p style="color:var(--color-body-text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">
          Each maturity number describes a different kind of second-half energy. Find yours below.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {maturityNumbers.map(item => (
            <a href={item.link} class="card-light overflow-hidden hover:border-violet/60 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 group block" style="text-decoration:none;">
              <div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
                <img src={["11","22","33"].includes(item.num) ? `/images/learn/master-numbers/Master Number - ${{11:"The Intuitive",22:"The Master Builder",33:"The Master Teacher"}[item.num]}.webp` : `/images/learn/maturity-number/Maturity Number - ${item.num}.webp`} alt={`Maturity Number ${item.num}`} class="w-full" style="aspect-ratio:2/3;object-fit:cover;display:block;width:100%;" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
              </div>
              <div style="padding:1.25rem;">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
                  <div style="font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-size:2.25rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-soft-gold);line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;">{item.num}</div>
                  <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-family-heading);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-body-text);margin:0;" class="group-hover:text-violet transition-colors">{item.title}</h3>
